  "texts": [
    "Suppose T t k and S t k are the trend and seasonal components at the end of the k th iteration of the inner loop, respectively.",
    "Steps of computing T t k+1 and S t k+1 for the (k + 1) th inner loop are detailed as follows:Step 1: Detrending.",
    "Computing the detrend seriesY detrend t = Y t -T k t.If there is a missing Y t at a time step, then the Y detrend t of that time step is also missing; Step 2: Seasonal smoothing.",
    "Smoothing the Y detrend t with a smoother using Loess to figure out the initial seasonal component S k+1 t; Step 3: Filtering with low-pass.",
    "Processing S k+1 t with a filter with low-pass and a subsequent using Loess to figure out any residual trend component T k+1 t; Step 4: Detrending."
  ],
  "correct_citations": []
}